{"questionId":"12182","questionHtml":"<p>Hence prove your conjectures in part (e).</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\\,{\\text{sin}}\\,x + b\\,{\\text{cos}}\\,x = \\sqrt {{a^2} + {b^2}} \\left( {{\\text{sin}}\\,\\theta \\,{\\text{sin}}\\,x + {\\text{cos}}\\,\\theta \\,{\\text{cos}}\\,x} \\right)\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>sin</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>cos</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>a</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>+</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>b</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </msqrt>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>sin</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>θ</mi>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>sin</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>cos</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>θ</mi>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>cos</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\\,{\\text{sin}}\\,x + b\\,{\\text{cos}}\\,x = \\sqrt {{a^2} + {b^2}} \\left( {{\\text{cos}}\\left( {x - \\theta } \\right)} \\right)\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>sin</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>cos</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>a</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>+</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>b</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </msqrt>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>cos</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>θ</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>So&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"A = \\sqrt {{a^2} + {b^2}} \">\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>a</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>+</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>b</mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </msqrt>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"B = 1\">\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"D = 0\">\n  <mi>D</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>And&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"C =&nbsp; - \\theta \">\n  <mi>C</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>So&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmln